Key Characteristics

Atlantic's value investing methodology is differentiated by:

Liquidity
Maintain liquidity to allow for opportunistic trading around core positions
Consistency
Strict adherence to a well-defined, and time-tested investment approach without style drift
Integrity
With all stakeholders,all the time
Collaboration
Global knowledge sharingacross geographies and sectors
Conviction
Concentrate capital and research on highest conviction investment ideas
Constructive Shareholder Activism
Engage with company management and board to enhance and accelerate shareholder value
Value InvestingApproach
Methodical identification of undervalued equities aroundthe world





